metadata.name: Onoromicon #13
metadata.description:
Landscapes of an imaginary world with colorful hills and rivers made of beziers and shaders.

made with P5js.

- 11 possible regions with different color schemes.
- Possible presence of water, clouds and rain.
- Maximum of 3 exterior planets visible.
- Astronaut Dave is lost somewhere on the planet.
